OL,3,CPorridge pots recalled amid fears of
OL,4,Cmouse contamination
OL,6,FSeveral Moma-branded porridge pots
OL,7,Fhave been recalled amid fears they may
OL,8,Fhave been contaminated by mice at
OL,9,Ftheir manufacturing site.
OL,11,FMoma issued a warning on Monday about
OL,12,Fseven of its pots and two of its
OL,13,Fporridge sachets.
OL,15,FCustomers have been told not to eat
OL,16,Fthe affected products and to return
OL,17,Fthem to the place of purchase for a
OL,18,Ffull refund.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
