OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774307469
OL,3,CPorridge pots recalled amid fears of
OL,4,Cmouse contamination
OL,6,FThe Food Standards Agency (FSA) said:
OL,7,F"Moma Foods is recalling various
OL,8,Fporridge pots and sachet products
OL,9,Fbecause of possible mouse
OL,10,Fcontamination at the manufacturing
OL,11,Fsite."
OL,13,FIt added: "These products may contain
OL,14,Fmouse contamination making them unsafe
OL,15,Fto eat."
OL,17,FNotices will be displayed in all
OL,18,Fretail stores selling the items and an
OL,19,Falert has been displayed on Moma's
OL,20,Fwebsite.
