OL,3,CPorridge pots recalled amid fears of
OL,4,Cmouse contamination
OL,6,FWhat has been recalled?
OL,8,FThe following MOMA-branded products
OL,9,Fhave been recalled
OL,11,FMoma has also asked customers to
OL,12,Freturn their almond butter and salted
OL,13,Fcaramel porridge sachets, and the
OL,14,Fapple, cinnamon and brown sugar
OL,15,Fsachets.
OL,17,FNone of its other products are
OL,18,Faffected.
